dsystem-this-is-happening-what-do-you-think-778717">&#39;This Is Happening&#39;</a> .</p><p> In <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lcd-soundsystem-glastonbury-2024-pyramid-review-setlist-photos-3769986">a five-star review of LCD Soundsystem&#39;s set at Glastonbury 2024</a> , <em>NME</em> wrote: “The packed-out Pyramid field hold each other tight and reach for the sky as LCD&#39;s 10 song masterclass naturally ends with &#39;All My Friends&#39;. This song and this moment are the manifestation of <a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">Glastonbury</a> at its best, the memories in the making and the good times still to come: &#39; <em>And if the sun comes up and I still don&#39;t wanna stagger home, then it&#39;s the memory of our betters that are keeping us on our feet</em> .&#39; That&#39;s how it starts.</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lcd-soundsystem-seem-to-be-teasing-a-london-gig-with-projections-around-shoreditch-you-are-here-again-3841144">LCD Soundsystem seem to be teasing a London gig with projections around Shoreditch: “You are here (again)”</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
